lead_paragraph: Coach Steve Hansen named just two uncapped players in his squad for the All Blacks' test against Wales on Saturday, their first match since the team lost six stalwarts following last year's World Cup triumph in England.

headline.print_headline: All Blacks' Hansen Names Just Two Uncapped Players to Face Wales
